main.java.com.raylabz.javaasynctask

Class AsyncTask<Parameter,Progress,Result>

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.com.raylabz.javaasynctask.AsyncTask<Parameter,Progress,Result>

  • public abstract class AsyncTask<Parameter,Progress,Result>
extends Object
    Implements the Android SDK AsyncTask for plain Java applications, as found in https://developer.android.com/reference/android/os/AsyncTask. Important note: Do not use this with the Android SDK, use the native AsyncTask instead. This package is destined for use in plain Java applications ONLY - Java SDKs are NOT supported. Created by RayLabz - 2019 Visit http://www.RayLabz.com Java AsyncTask - A port of Android SDK's AsyncTask for plain Java. Perform background operations and publish results on the UI thread without working with threads and handlers. Repository: https://github.com/RayLabz/Java-AsyncTask Guide: https://RayLabz.github.io/Java-AsyncTask
